{"tid":307592,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2018嘅白川鄉幾時點燈","createTime":"2017-07-03T13:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T13:52:41.000Z","uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef922256de84b56d4599b64e20c792d8f0857d0b","tid":307592,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"想買平機票去旅行玩下雪 但sem break係十二月尾到一月中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知出年一月頭白川鄉點燈未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2017點燈日子如下：<br />\n1月 22 23 29 30<br />\n2月 5 6<br />\n<br />\n我上google揾原來未出2018時間表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下如果無點燈嘅白川鄉夜晚到底係點 上網揾嘅圖都係點咗燈<br />\n同埋想問下一月頭嘅北陸積雪夠唔夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fc95467639ad3f7d43ca2ff0de5a7c388dd7ee","tid":307592,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec08f4f5102f0546d98a62e291612b42cbc3436e","tid":307592,"uid":30457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"年年都係一月下旬<br />\n冇點燈咪普通一個鄉下地方<br />\n一般都夠雪 <br />\n2016個年無記錯好似點燈前一兩日先持續大雪"}]}